{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8d06705e-9607-49c1-bb09-8dabb2223ee9","content":"**Yes, you will hit a compatibility issue.** MSTest v4 (the `MSTest` 4.x meta-package) requires **.NET 8.0 or later** — it dropped support for `net6.0`.\n\nYour options:\n\n1. **Upgrade your target framework** to `net8.0` (or newer), then update to MSTest v4.\n2. **Stay on MSTest v3** (`3.8.x`) if you need to keep targeting `net6.0`.\n\n> Note: .NET 6 itself reached end-of-support in November 2024, so upgrading to `net8.0`+ is recommended regardless.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c94a5b14-6fb1-47b3-a43a-129a850b48c7","outputTokens":153},"id":"2fb1c639-8813-4885-8b2c-25b769c964a1","timestamp":"2026-04-05T01:02:01.606Z","parentId":"ced4bea6-5eef-4873-9a62-002f36725b78"}
